{"title":"不灭的灵魂","authors":["侯龙柱"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":3,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"不灭的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯龙柱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十二岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能用时间的尺码来衡量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像他的精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨越年龄的界限"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨越时空的距离"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如三月的阳光和鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放在每个季节里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是五千年文明孕育的骄子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是铁锤和镰刀塑成的雕像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每个时代的窗口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你都能看见他的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每条崎岖的路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你都会与他一路同行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他使陌生变得亲切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使每颗心成为太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂地挂满人类的大树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每次求助的呼声中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每场危难的险境里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们都会发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就是雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从他圣洁的目光里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着他的气息走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是他不灭的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不灭的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已走进了千万人的心中"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}